headline: Google, Nvidia, Lilly Lead 5 Stocks Near Buy Points
summary: Google-parent Alphabet, Nvidia and Eli Lilly, a trio of trillion-dollar companies, lead this weekend's watch list of five stocks near buy points.  Toll Brothers is the No. 1-rated stock in the Building-Residential/Commercial industry group, according to IBD Stock Checkup.

headline: Guggenheim Reduces PT on Eli Lilly and Company (LLY) to $1,161, Reiterates ‘Buy’ Rating
summary: Eli Lilly and Company (NYSE:LLY) is one of the best stocks to buy and hold for 20 years.
